list.abstract: solo，游戏术语，源于竞技游戏，常用来指单挑。如《魔兽争霸》建造模式就是典型的solo，还比如《真·三国无双》中的中法，《DOTA》中的1v1单中，也是solo的一种。另外该词也用于调侃一些不懂装懂的菜鸟。
《SOLO》是一首韩语流行嘻哈歌曲，由韩国女歌手金智妮演唱，TEDDY作词，TEDDY和24作曲，24编曲。于2018年11月12日由YG Entertainment发行，收录于专辑《SOLO》中。

yingyinNormal.en: Hilary Clinton was there to cut the ribbon, I got to play solo.
yingyinNormal.zh: 希拉里还去剪彩了，我独奏了一曲。

yingyinNormal.en: And a year later he goes back to the Reno. And he steps up on that stage and he plays the best motherfucking solo the world has ever heard.
yingyinNormal.zh: 一年后他回到舞台上，吹出了有史以来最他妈牛逼的独奏。

yingyinNormal.en: You are the Han Solo that fought with the Rebellion.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你是大名鼎鼎的汉·索洛，和义军并肩作战过。

yingyinNormal.en: Solo, what is she doing? I don't know. But it ain't good.
yingyinNormal.zh: 索洛，她在干什么？我不知道，但肯定不是好事。

yingyinNormal.en: This is the Millennium Falcon? You're Han Solo? I used to be.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这艘船是千年隼号？你就是汉·索洛？我曾经是。

yingyinNormal.en: Han Solo, the Rebellion general? No, the smuggler. Wasn't he a war hero?
yingyinNormal.zh: 汉·索洛，那个义军将军？不，是走私犯。他不是个战斗英雄吗？

yingyinNormal.en: So he executed a solo rescue mission, which failed. This is his last transmission.
yingyinNormal.zh: 于是他单独执行了营救任务，结果失败了。这是他最后传送的消息。

yingyinNormal.en: Now you're just trying to take over the whole thing. You know, maybe I should go solo.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你现在就是想独揽一切，或许我该单飞。

yingyinNormal.en: Who stole it from me! Well, you tell him that Han Solo just stole back the Millennium Falcon for good.
yingyinNormal.zh: 他偷的我的，你告诉他汉·索洛如今又把千年隼偷回来了，不会再丢了。

yingyinNormal.en: Interesting, but isn't ventriloquism by definition a solo activity? Yeah. Tell me another interest of yours.
yingyinNormal.zh: 有意思，但口技不是个人娱乐项目吗？再说个兴趣爱好。

yingyinNormal.en: Gentlemen, use your imagination. Innovate. Did Han Solo let Luke Skywalker freeze to death on the ice planet of Hoth?
yingyinNormal.zh: 先生们，想象一下，创新，韩梭罗让天行者卢克冻死在冰雪星球霍斯上了吗？

examination_example.sentence: It first appeared over 3,000 years ago and stands for China's <highlight>solo</highlight> musical instrument tradition.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 它最早出现在3000多年前，代表着中国的独奏乐器传统。

examination_example.sentence: Copeland won her first national competition as a <highlight>solo</highlight> performer.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 科普兰作为独唱演员赢得了她的第一次全国比赛。

examination_example.sentence: In 2007, she became a <highlight>solo</highlight> (单独的) performer, and in 2015 she became its principal dancer.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 2007年，她成为独舞表演者，2015年，她成为其首席舞者。
